				<wikidot:authorName>Uncle Nicolini</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3487700</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Okay! So this whole ordeal started late last night (as most things do) when <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1549471892" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" >Captain Kirby</a></span> and I were talking. I jokingly do 'Panda Watch 2k19' updates on whatever mundane things my dog is doing, and he commented that it would be a fun SCP idea to have a website that shows you the last thing your dog did. We brainstormed this one out together and I wrote it while he continued to pour good ideas into my noggin.</p> <p>So hooray, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1549471892" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" >Captain Kirby</a></span> and nico collab. Woo!</p> <p>All pet pictures are courtesty of <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gabriel-jade" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=414239&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1549471892" alt="Gabriel Jade" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=414239)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gabriel-jade" >Gabriel Jade</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/9volt" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2800867&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1549471892" alt="9Volt" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2800867)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/9volt" >9Volt</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4022320&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1549471892" alt="RockTeethMothEyes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4022320)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" >RockTeethMothEyes</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alces-alces" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4057128&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1549471892" alt="Alces_alces" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4057128)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alces-alces" >Alces_alces</a></span> respectively.<br /> Nala's picture is from here- <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Dirt_and_Mud_002_-_Loose_Dirt_with_Plants.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Dirt_and_Mud_002_-_Loose_Dirt_with_Plants.jpg</a><br /> and the Jamba Juice is from here <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/12739382@N04/2415197699">https://www.flickr.com/photos/12739382@N04/2415197699</a></p> <p>Special thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/woedenaz" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404096&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1549471892" alt="Woedenaz" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404096)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/woedenaz" >Woedenaz</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4022320&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1549471892" alt="RockTeethMothEyes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4022320)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" >RockTeethMothEyes</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-dragon" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2325849&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1549471892" alt="Dr Dragon" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2325849)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-dragon" >Dr Dragon</a></span> for crit.</p> 
